Comment: 10,0:00:05.22,0:00:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on!
Comment: 10,0:00:06.72,0:00:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait, Diana! I said I couldn't accept this!
Comment: 10,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please talk to me!
Comment: 10,0:00:11.74,0:00:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with making a decision just like that?
Comment: 10,0:00:15.48,0:00:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you regret it?
Comment: 10,0:00:17.52,0:00:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As I have already said, this is of\Nno concern to you. The matter is settled.{## "no business speaking up" is a bit harsh maybe}
Comment: 10,0:00:23.79,0:00:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Comment: 10,0:00:24.78,0:00:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right in that Kagari Atsuko is an outsider.
Comment: 10,0:00:28.52,0:00:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite that, she traveled a long distance simply to speak with you.
Comment: 10,0:00:32.59,0:00:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you not at least hear her out?
Comment: 10,0:00:35.36,0:00:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time for that.
Comment: 10,0:00:39.08,0:00:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana, think it through! Isn't there anything you've left undone at Luna Nova?
Comment: 10,0:00:44.63,0:00:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even one.{## or just "don't you have things..." -- "i don't"}{hope it's okay}
Comment: 10,0:02:22.38,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those of Cavendish blood are permitted to enter the shrine.
Comment: 10,0:02:27.64,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She said there was no time left.\NIs there some reason she has to hurry?
Comment: 10,0:02:32.43,0:02:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to explain.
Comment: 10,0:02:34.39,0:02:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It manifests in the glow of the horn adorning\Nthe family's patron beast, the white unicorn.{## maybe without "in the glow of"}
Comment: 10,0:02:39.83,0:02:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Gem of Venus's radiance is obscured,{## astronomy lingo just because; here's the issue though, the gem lights up in the highlight scene later whereas this says venus conceals/obscures the horn's radiance; this is a direct contradiction that needs to be resolved one way or another}{you know what, I'm just going to reverse this}
Comment: 10,0:02:43.69,0:02:50.35,Default,,15,15,0,,the seal on the shrine is undone, allowing she who\Nswears upon her ancestors' souls to become the family head.{## might have a plot reason but you don't really unleash seals i guess}
Comment: 10,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gem of Venus?
