Comment: 10,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, today is the Venusian eclipse. {nobody writes about this, only venus transits. also naisu wordcraft}
Comment: 10,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Venusian eclipse?
