Comment: 10,0:04:52.34,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This choice of hers must have come\Nafter thorough deliberation.
Comment: 10,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too, but...
Comment: 10,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, her stubbornness won't allow her to go back on her word.
Comment: 10,0:05:03.27,0:05:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there only one reasonable option?\NYou have to respect her feelings.
Comment: 10,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Comment: 10,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you said was right.
Comment: 10,0:05:13.01,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still can't accept it! Something's wrong with Diana just quitting school!
Comment: 10,0:05:17.55,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just your own selfish desires speaking?
Comment: 10,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it is...
Comment: 10,0:05:22.60,0:05:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can tell that Diana doesn't want to quit school.
Comment: 10,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she won't talk to anyone about it...
Comment: 10,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell?
Comment: 10,0:05:31.47,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say it yourself? Diana would never abandon something halfway through.
