Comment: 10,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So why would she just go and drop out?
Comment: 10,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Comment: 10,0:05:43.69,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, Diana could do everything from the start, and maybe there wasn't anything left for her to learn.
Comment: 10,0:05:49.30,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But Diana wouldn't have come to Luna Nova if she didn't have a reason!
Comment: 10,0:05:52.37,0:05:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She was researching the Words and Grand Triskelion...{## "the Grand Triskelion"? with the article?}{I avoided it since I think it was revealed they're kind of the same or related}
