Comment: 10,0:06:14.07,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:06:15.41,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was back when we were children. I'm not so sure of the details myself.
Comment: 10,0:06:19.29,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All the adults were talking about how\NDiana might never use magic again.
Comment: 10,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Comment: 10,0:06:25.31,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, she never gave up.
Comment: 10,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She forewent playing with the children her age.
Comment: 10,0:06:32.28,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All her time was wholeheartedly\Ndevoted to the practice of magic.{## makes for a nicer linebreak is all}
Comment: 10,0:06:38.67,0:06:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even I know what lit such a passion in her.
