Comment: 10,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about her being alone. {in a repetitious in a repetitious mood I see}
Comment: 10,0:07:14.98,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so am I...
