Comment: 10,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Mama!
Comment: 10,0:07:47.89,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mama, don't forget what Diana's like.
Comment: 10,0:07:50.54,0:07:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she should still be able to break through lesser magic.{## is this getting associated with satanism too much? i mean, the association kinda works but i don't want to force it in when it's not intended here}{your brain works in mysterious ways. light means karui, not hikari}
Comment: 10,0:07:54.52,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry. Nobody can escape the grip of my snakes.
Comment: 10,0:07:59.66,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about performing the ritual—Diana will run out of time before she even reaches the shrine.
Comment: 10,0:08:05.75,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already anxious to see the look on her arrogant little face come tomorrow morning.
Comment: 10,0:08:17.38,0:08:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why did you return this late at night?
Comment: 10,0:08:20.13,0:08:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Diana's in trouble! You need to let me in!
Comment: 10,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What ridiculous—
Comment: 10,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Comment: 10,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lord Andrew?
Comment: 10,0:08:27.57,0:08:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We overheard Daryl speaking with her daughters.
Comment: 10,0:08:30.47,0:08:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She did something to prevent\NDiana from performing the ritual.
Comment: 10,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Daryl did?
Comment: 10,0:08:34.57,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She said Diana wouldn't even be able to reach the shrine.
Comment: 10,0:08:37.29,0:08:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just past this door, isn't it?
Comment: 10,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to let me through!
Comment: 10,0:08:41.70,0:08:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot. It is our custom that only members of the House of Cavendish may pass.
Comment: 10,0:08:46.64,0:08:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for that stuff! Something bad\Nmight be happening to Diana as we speak!
Comment: 10,0:08:51.16,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency. If they really stopped Diana, it'll soon be too late!
Comment: 10,0:08:55.40,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,H-However, it is said that a horrific calamity\Nwill befall those who disturb the ritual!
Comment: 10,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Open...!
Comment: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Mở ra đi...
Comment: 10,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help!
Comment: 10,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You wait here, Andrew.
Comment: 10,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Comment: 10,0:09:23.79,0:09:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a witch too, you know. I'm strong against calamities.
Comment: 10,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to bring Diana back.
Comment: 10,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Comment: 10,0:09:32.39,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind! The customs—
Comment: 10,0:09:36.79,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Customs are made to be broken!
Comment: 10,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Metamorphie Faciesse!
Comment: 10,0:10:08.91,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there...
Comment: 10,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Comment: 10,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Metamorphie Faciesse!
Comment: 10,0:10:35.90,0:10:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How's that?!
Comment: 10,0:10:41.83,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Comment: 10,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Comment: 10,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow!
Comment: 10,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that poison?
Comment: 10,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing on Sucy's!
Comment: 10,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Metamorphie Faciesse!
Comment: 10,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:11:19.78,0:11:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko... Akko!
Comment: 10,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you awakened?
Comment: 10,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana...
Comment: 10,0:11:30.81,0:11:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see there are simply no limits to your absurdity.
Comment: 10,0:11:34.18,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to save you...
Comment: 10,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Comment: 10,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, every time I feel as though\NI've grown accustomed to you...
Comment: 10,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You continue to astonish me in unexpected ways.
Comment: 10,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana, what about the ritual?!
Comment: 10,0:11:51.73,0:11:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I left for the shrine now, \Nthe Venusian eclipse would be long over.
Comment: 10,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, it can't be...
Comment: 10,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you leave me behind?
