Comment: 10,0:12:02.86,0:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't possibly leave you to deal with your injuries.
Comment: 10,0:12:07.04,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, weren't you attempting to persuade me to not perform the ritual?
