Comment: 10,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all so much...
Comment: 10,0:13:09.63,0:13:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Comment: 10,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All 1,500 years of the history of the Cavendish line.{## how do they keep their name with female heads?}{by... keeping their name? you can just do that}
Comment: 10,0:13:14.03,0:13:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,These books represent the culmination of my predecessors' research
Comment: 10,0:13:17.74,0:13:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,about countless forms of healing magic.
Comment: 10,0:13:21.27,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, many of them have become obsolete\Nwith the advance of the medical sciences.
Comment: 10,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she...
Comment: 10,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Nine Olde Witches?
Comment: 10,0:13:35.16,0:13:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cavendish foremother, Beatrix the Witch.
Comment: 10,0:13:39.30,0:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Her magic saved the lives of innumerable people.
Comment: 10,0:13:43.28,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She also created our founding motto, "Compassion".{## in the light of this episode, we should've gone with "compassion" for jiai}{we can just batch it}
Comment: 10,0:13:48.35,0:13:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We live in a time of peace,\Nand this place has not been used in years.
Comment: 10,0:13:52.57,0:13:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother Bernadette worked hard\Nto ensure it would remain this way.
Comment: 10,0:13:57.11,0:13:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother?
Comment: 10,0:14:00.61,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a weak constitution, and after years of pushing herself, she passed away all too soon.{## comma splice; also consider "she paid the highest price" as a poetic edit, like in that church anthem}
Comment: 10,0:14:09.76,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly proud of what my mother and ancestors did, and of the Cavendish name.
Comment: 10,0:14:18.91,0:14:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Comment: 10,0:14:21.09,0:14:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to protect it, to preserve this home...
Comment: 10,0:14:30.14,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up! You can still protect this house!
Comment: 10,0:14:35.01,0:14:38.48,Default,,15,15,0,,It's already over! There's no chance of making it now—
Comment: 10,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say that until you go—until you try!
Comment: 10,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There {\fax-0.2}must{\i0} be a way!
Comment: 10,0:14:45.07,0:14:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you had such a heartfelt dream.
Comment: 10,0:14:49.62,0:14:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing! That's a wonderful dream!
Comment: 10,0:14:52.01,0:14:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just give up on a dream\Nthat's so important to you!
Comment: 10,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect what's precious to you!
Comment: 10,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Comment: 10,0:14:59.77,0:15:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then come back to school too!
Comment: 10,0:15:02.57,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:15:03.31,0:15:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do both—be the head and attend school! That's the best option!
Comment: 10,0:15:07.93,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it would be impossible to—
Comment: 10,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\fax-0.2}can{\i0} do it!
Comment: 10,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone can do it, it's you!
Comment: 10,0:15:13.68,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Believe in yourself and your heart!
Comment: 10,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Believe in... my heart...
Comment: 10,0:15:23.14,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff... is a Word nearby?
Comment: 10,0:15:26.85,0:15:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When traditional and modern powers mingle,\Nthe gate to an unseen world will open.
Comment: 10,0:15:32.74,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a saying that has been passed down\Nthroughout the generations.
Comment: 10,0:15:36.33,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the fifth Word, the one related to history?
Comment: 10,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, recite it!
Comment: 10,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sybilladura Lelladybura.
Comment: 10,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sybilladura.
Comment: 10,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sybilladura...
Comment: 10,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lelladybura!
Comment: 10,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lelladybura!
Comment: 10,0:16:01.74,0:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Comment: 10,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Chariot's broom, the Shiny Volley! {...okay?}{## sure let's go with that}
Comment: 10,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, Diana!
Comment: 10,0:16:11.96,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Traditional and modern powers...\Nand a gate to the unknown. {then why does she say "uneen gate"?}
Comment: 10,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, let's go together!
Comment: 10,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay!
Comment: 10,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia Freyre!
Comment: 10,0:17:10.76,0:17:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Comment: 10,0:17:11.67,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana, that means we made it!
Comment: 10,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you go...
Comment: 10,0:17:33.47,0:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Any further than this!
Comment: 10,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aeguil! {e-guuiru}{## let's go with that!}
Comment: 10,0:17:51.30,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the ritual shrine?
Comment: 10,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I said we wouldn't let you go!
Comment: 10,0:18:15.12,0:18:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the horrific calamity that\Nbefalls those who disturb the ritual?
Comment: 10,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana...
Comment: 10,0:18:22.68,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Save us!
Comment: 10,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Save us...
Comment: 10,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Comment: 10,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be... the remaining time? {sorry}
Comment: 10,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry! Diana!
Comment: 10,0:18:35.73,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana? Hey, Diana!
Comment: 10,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ennor Fiendennor!{enno-ru fiendino-ru  so I guess maybe nore}
Comment: 10,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Beatrix? {first use of this}
Comment: 10,0:19:45.09,0:19:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana...
Comment: 10,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady.
Comment: 10,0:19:59.71,0:20:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was unable to complete the ritual.
Comment: 10,0:20:02.84,0:20:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very end, I made the determination to abandon it.
Comment: 10,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not regret my decision.
Comment: 10,0:20:12.14,0:20:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, please stop pretending\Nas though you've forgotten.
Comment: 10,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to be reserved.
Comment: 10,0:20:21.06,0:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pursue the dream you have had ever since your childhood.
Comment: 10,0:20:26.71,0:20:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I must also suggest you return to Luna Nova.{it's more forceful}
Comment: 10,0:20:29.82,0:20:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 10,0:20:30.86,0:20:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon my rudeness, but you no longer have any reason to stay here.
Comment: 10,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Comment: 10,0:20:36.75,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you can once again return to the manor, \Nwe will protect it in your stead.{## according to my cursory research, venusian eclipses happen 8 years apart every 120 years, so eclipse - eight years - eclipse - 120 years - eclipse - eight years etc; good luck diana}{it's a magic moon, it must happen more often}
Comment: 10,0:20:43.22,0:20:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, follow the path you yourself wish to walk.
Comment: 10,0:20:59.81,0:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone... thank you.
Comment: 10,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Daryl!
Comment: 10,0:21:16.71,0:21:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's too obsessed with her Cavendish pride.\NWhat a thoroughly charmless child.
Comment: 10,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is my sister's daughter, in that regard.{## see ep19 2146; also she has the cavendish eyes now}
Comment: 10,0:21:26.49,0:21:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that may just allow her to revive the Cavendish family one day.
Comment: 10,0:21:35.01,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm certain.
Comment: 10,0:21:45.65,0:21:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari Atsuko, how could you possibly forget this?
Comment: 10,0:21:52.51,0:21:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I got you to give me a lift home.
Comment: 10,0:21:55.65,0:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko.
Comment: 10,0:21:56.46,0:21:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Comment: 10,0:21:57.87,0:22:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing that I cannot leave unsaid.
Comment: 10,0:22:01.34,0:22:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What now, did I mess up again somehow?!
Comment: 10,0:22:07.94,0:22:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I must say... I'm grateful for what you did.
Comment: 10,0:22:12.70,0:22:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Comment: 10,0:22:14.89,0:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? What did you just say?!
Comment: 10,0:22:17.73,0:22:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not repeat myself.
Comment: 10,0:22:19.47,0:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I really couldn't hear! Say it again!
Comment: 10,0:22:22.20,0:22:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not.
Comment: 10,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more time!
Comment: 10,0:22:24.63,0:22:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will absolutely {\fax-0.2}not{\i0} say it!
Comment: 10,0:22:26.30,0:22:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so bashful!
Comment: 10,0:22:27.99,0:22:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drop you!{## just saying, this is chav slang for knocking someone out, in case you want to use something else instead}{it's just bantz}
